hideroot

The kernel module for avoid rooting detection on android.

You must change uid on source code. (hideroot.c:42)

root@android:/storage/emulated/legacy # ps | grep love
u0_a249   12367 284   959288 70932 ffffffff 40303fe8 S klb.android.lovelive

it's uid is 10249.


To compile:

make -C {KERNELDIR} M=$PWD

To use:
adb push hideroot.ko /sdcard/
adb shell insmod /sdcard/hideroot.ko

